<br />
A hasted, dual wielding tank/melee will hit about twice a second, depending upon mob ac. That's 120 hits per minute.
<br />

<br />
The maths of this would be immensely over-powering:
<br />

<br />
120 x 50 x 6 = 36,000 damage (@ 100dps) !!!
<br />

<br />
Very nice idea tho, and high recast would prevent total imbalance. I would imagine increasing the mana cost to ~600, and damage to about 10 per hit would be better balanced. (+20dps with about 7200 damage over time ... assuming the tank doesn't die)<br />_________________<br />-- I used to be an atheist until I became an Arch Convoker ~ <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=535614" target="_blank" class="postlink">Ducalio "Fivehead" Jeebus</a>--</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
	</tr>
