				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I did a small study on this somewhere before. Wont go searching for it, but if I remember correctly,
<br />

<br />
At approx lvl 30, DS ratio to avg mob HPs were about 1:100
<br />
At 65 (excluding green and light blue old world farming), DS ratio to avg mob HPs were about 1:440.
<br />

<br />
So to get the ratios back it line, a 65 mage would need at or close to a 200 point dmg sheild to bring the ratio back to where it was in the mid 30's range. 
<br />

<br />
That was the gist of it.  <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile" border="0" /><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=394587"> Sillaen 65th Arch Convoker</a><br>Cazic Thule.
